document.full_text: oman plans to spend 1 billion rials ($2.6 billion) to "satisfy the demands" of street protesters in the gulf arab country who seek jobs and political reforms, state television reported on sunday.
document.title: oman to spend $2.6 billion to satisfy protest demands
